description: She was hit with a brutal seven-figure legal bill at London's High Court last week, marking the end of the long-running Wagatha Christie libel battle. But Rebekah Vardy has finally had some good news.
title: Wagatha Wars II as Rebekah lands fly-on-the-wall show of her own... and if husband Jamie ends up at Wrexham, she might get to do a double act with Blake Lively

description: ROBERT HARDMAN: When Charles III came to the throne in September 2022, some commentators warned he would seek to 'meddle' and 'cross constitutional red lines'.
title: As he becomes the first monarch in 50 years to open Canada's parliament... If anyone knows how to walk this political tightrope, it's the King, writes ROBERT HARDMAN

description: Bella Hadid's raunchy 2024 Cannes Film Festival outfit was used as an example of what not to wear to this year's ceremony, sources claim.
title: Bella Hadid's raunchy 2024 Cannes Film Festival outfit was 'used as an example of what NOT to wear to this year's event' - after annual ceremony banned risqué outfits

description: With viewing figures now on the slide, Good Morning Britain is facing the biggest overhaul in its 11-year history as bosses try to cut costs.
title: Fears of 'mutiny' as Good Morning Britain faces biggest overhaul in its 11-year history in effort to cut costs

description: ROSS CLARK: You can almost sense the jubilation on the faces of EU negotiators as they eye up our fish and dream up ways to trap Britain in their regulatory claws
title: ROSS CLARK: Like a teacher's pet, Starmer is a stickler for rules... which is why I fear he will doom Britain to a sorry future as an EU satellite

description: The troubled singer released a statement on Thursday, insisting he was not one of Diddy's victims.
title: Strained Justin Bieber breaks cover after addressing Diddy abuse claims amid rumored money woes
